name: custom return address stamp
description:
paper & ink original designed return address stamp customized with your return address. choose a design and include your address and information with your order*. in a couple of days, i will send you a proof via email of your stamp. once the design is approved, the stamp will be made and shipped to you! 

• about 1.5 x 3" depending on the style
• rubber stamp with wooden handle

please feel free to email me with any questions or details... paperandink@hotmail.com

*include "note to seller" in the paypal section indicating your design choice and address information.

name: lucca letterpress announcement
description:
a customized letterpress birth announcement. each announcement has the baby's name in hand written script spanning across the width of the announcement. three hand cut fabric leaves sprout from the the end of the writing adding a touch of spring. a hand sewn fabric pocket is applied to the back of the announcement to enclose a 3x5 photo of the new baby. the baby's birth information and family greeting are added to the front in clean block typeface. each announcement is printed by hand with your color choice of ink on double ply, soft white, 100% cotton museum board. 

$7.50 each is for an order of 200 pieces. 

for detailed photos go to... http://bbpaperandink.blogspot.com/2011/07/birth-announcement.html

-size A6 (4 1/2 x 6 1/4) 
-turnaround time is approximately 4 weeks.
-2 proofs allowed, each additional proof is $20. once the art is approved, the final proof is then sent to have a copper letterpress plate made and further changes to the text cannot be made.  

please feel free to contact me if you have any questions or to submit all custom information.

name: mateo ocean birth announcement
description:
a ocean themed birth announcement. sea creature details adorn this whimsical birth announcement with a mix of with hand embroidery, fabric applique, pinhole art and hand painting. your baby's name is written in hand embroidery just to the right of your baby's photo. the baby's birth information is added to the front in modern typeface while the seahorse playfully delivers the family's greeting in hand drawn lettering. each announcement is then digitally printed on heavy, soft white card stock. 

announcements include light gray envelopes lined with coordinating light blue french knot dotted liner, accented with a friendly crab. envelopes are printed with your return address.

minimum order 20 pieces. 
announcements are flat printed from one original artpiece, so the finished cards and envelope liners do not have dimensional sewing on each individual announcement.
 
to see more photos go to... http://bbpaperandink.blogspot.com/2011/05/baby-announcement.html

-size A7 (5x7)
-turnaround time is approximately 2 weeks. 2 proofs allowed, each additional proof is $20. please contact me for pricing on numbers not listed and to submit all custom information.

name: silvered linen panel
description: 16x16 linen panel. 100% unbleached linen stretched over 3/4 inch traditional artists wooden stretcher bars. linen is silver leafed. sold individually or in multiples as pictured. hang on the wall as is, the silver leaf brings a beautiful reflective quality to the room. also available in custom sizes... contact me for pricing and special orders.

name: 6 twig letters
description:
birch twig  letters mounted on a sliced birch base.
base measures from 1 1/4 to 1 1/2 inches, letter measures 1 3/4 inches high.
perfect for place settings at a wedding, party or just on a shelf.
handmade to order, green, pink or neutral thread. custom thread colors available to match your event. turnaround is approximately 1 week. 
shipping will be determined by the number of letters ordered. be sure to indicate which letters you would like at checkout.
